                        <title>From a Biosynthetic Pathway toward a Biocatalytic Process and Chemocatalytic Modifications: Three‐Step Enzymatic Cascade to the Plant Metabolite            cis            ‐(+)‐12‐OPDA and Metathesis‐Derived Products</title>
